casebody.data:
UNITED SERVICES, INC., Plaintiff-Respondent
v.
CITY OF NEWARK, Defendant-Movant. M-1472 September Term 2016
079452 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal is denied, but the Court requests the Superior Court, Law Division, to expedite the disposition of plaintiffs complaint.
